NAME        UDP-N-acetylglucosamine 4,6-dehydratase (configuration-retaining);
            PglF
CLASS       Lyases;
            Carbon-oxygen lyases;
            Hydro-lyases
SYSNAME     UDP-N-acetyl-alpha-D-glucosamine hydro-lyase (configuration-retaining; UDP-2-acetamido-2,6-dideoxy-alpha-D-xylo-hex-4-ulose-forming)
REACTION    UDP-N-acetyl-alpha-D-glucosamine = UDP-2-acetamido-2,6-dideoxy-alpha-D-xylo-hex-4-ulose + H2O [RN:R10266]
ALL_REAC    R10266
